name: Silver Sky - 8x8 Chickadee Print
description:
This is a fine art giclée print of an original painting by Linzy Arnott titled "Silver Sky". It is printed on 5x7" high quality gloss paper with archival inks. There is a white border for framing purposes. This print is signed on the back and beautifully packaged in a clear polyethylene re-sealable sleeve.

This print is also available in 8x10.

Ships flat in a bend proof secure mailer.

This painting was created as part of a series for my gallery show titled "Birds of a Feather" held at the Wallflower Gallery in Port Coquitlam BC Canada September-October 2010. 


copyright 2010 Linzy Arnott
